<p class="ft1411" style="position:absolute;top:532px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap">The prevailing currency for all transactions related to this Contract shall be the currency </p>
<p class="ft1414" style="position:absolute;top:554px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap">shown in (Contract data), while the exchange shall be in accordance with the provisions <br/>of this Contract and the financial procedures, laws and regulations approved by  the </p>
<p class="ft1411" style="position:absolute;top:598px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap">First Party. </p>
<p class="ft1412" style="position:absolute;top:620px;left:93px;white-space:nowrap"><b>4-6 </b></p>
<p class="ft1412" style="position:absolute;top:620px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap"><b>Clearance declaration </b></p>
<p class="ft1411" style="position:absolute;top:642px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap"> </p>
<p class="ft1411" style="position:absolute;top:642px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap">The  Second  Party  shall  submit  to  the  First  Party  a  written  declaration  in  the  form </p>
<p class="ft1411" style="position:absolute;top:664px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap">determined by the First Party, in which it proves that the final invoice constitutes the full </p>
<p class="ft1411" style="position:absolute;top:686px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap">and final settlement of all amounts owed to him under the Contract, and the clearance </p>
<p class="ft1411" style="position:absolute;top:708px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap">declaration is effective from that date. </p>
<p class="ft1412" style="position:absolute;top:730px;left:101px;white-space:nowrap"><b>5 </b></p>
<p class="ft1412" style="position:absolute;top:730px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap"><b>Obligations and Responsibilities of the Second Party </b></p>
<p class="ft1411" style="position:absolute;top:752px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap"> </p>
<p class="ft1411" style="position:absolute;top:752px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap">In addition to what is stipulated in the articles of this Contract and its appendices, the </p>
<p class="ft1411" style="position:absolute;top:774px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap">Second Party shall: </p>
<p class="ft1411" style="position:absolute;top:796px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap"> </p>
<p class="ft1411" style="position:absolute;top:796px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap">(A) Provide full cooperation and coordination with the representatives of the First Party </p>
<p class="ft1411" style="position:absolute;top:818px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap">and  its  representatives  and  the  relevant  authorities  in  everything  related  to  the </p>
<p class="ft1411" style="position:absolute;top:840px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap">provision of services of this Contract. </p>
<p class="ft1411" style="position:absolute;top:862px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap"> </p>
<p class="ft1411" style="position:absolute;top:862px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap">(B) Bear full responsibility for the performance of its obligations under this Contract </p>
<p class="ft1411" style="position:absolute;top:884px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap">according to the technical conditions and specifications and engineering designs in </p>
<p class="ft1411" style="position:absolute;top:906px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap">this Contract and in Appendix (4) (agreed scope of work) and Appendix (7) (technical </p>
<p class="ft1415" style="position:absolute;top:928px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap">specifications and criteria for evaluating the implementation of Works) agreed upon, <br/>and at the level of quality required by the First Party. </p>
<p class="ft1411" style="position:absolute;top:972px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap"> </p>
<p class="ft1411" style="position:absolute;top:972px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap">(C) Submit applications for obtaining the necessary licenses for work in accordance </p>
<p class="ft1411" style="position:absolute;top:994px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap">with the regular procedures (including government licenses) and renew them, and </p>
<p class="ft1411" style="position:absolute;top:1016px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap">he shall make the necessary efforts to obtain and receive them and maintain their </p>
<p class="ft1411" style="position:absolute;top:1038px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap">validity during the Contract duration. </p>
<p class="ft1411" style="position:absolute;top:1059px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap"> </p>
<p class="ft1411" style="position:absolute;top:1059px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap">(D) Submit applications and make efforts to obtain visas, work licenses, employment </p>
<p class="ft1411" style="position:absolute;top:1081px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap">permits, escorts permit and other necessary permits for individuals working on Work </p>
