<p class="ft1511" style="position:absolute;top:356px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap">issued by the First Party from time to time. </p>
<p class="ft1511" style="position:absolute;top:378px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap"> </p>
<p class="ft1511" style="position:absolute;top:378px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap">(H)  Comply  with  the  orders,  regulations,  and  instructions  issued  by  the  Ministry  of </p>
<p class="ft1511" style="position:absolute;top:400px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap">Human  Resources  and  Social  Development  notified  in  advance  to  Second  Party </p>
