<p class="ft1511" style="position:absolute;top:840px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap">(L) Ensure the correctness and integrity of information that may affect its ability to carry </p>
<p class="ft1511" style="position:absolute;top:862px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap">out work. </p>
<p class="ft1511" style="position:absolute;top:884px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap"> </p>
<p class="ft1511" style="position:absolute;top:884px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap">(M) Examine the rules and regulations applicable to the work. </p>
<p class="ft1511" style="position:absolute;top:906px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap"> </p>
<p class="ft1511" style="position:absolute;top:906px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap">(N) Commitment to quality specifications, security and safety standards while carrying </p>
<p class="ft1511" style="position:absolute;top:928px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap">out his duties. </p>
<p class="ft1511" style="position:absolute;top:950px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap"> </p>
<p class="ft1511" style="position:absolute;top:950px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap">(O) Adhere to the terms and conditions of local content in accordance with the terms </p>
<p class="ft1511" style="position:absolute;top:972px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap">of the Contract. </p>
<p class="ft1511" style="position:absolute;top:994px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap"> </p>
<p class="ft1511" style="position:absolute;top:994px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap">(P) The Second Party shall be responsible to the First Party for any damage, claim, or </p>
<p class="ft1511" style="position:absolute;top:1016px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap">any  issues,  procedures,  costs,  or  direct  expenses  resulting  from  any  third-party </p>
<p class="ft1514" style="position:absolute;top:1038px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap">claim filed against the First Party, or borne by the First Party related to any of the <br/>following cases: </p>
<p class="ft1511" style="position:absolute;top:1081px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap"> </p>
<p class="ft1511" style="position:absolute;top:1081px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap">  1. Poor performance in carrying out the Work stated in the Contract. </p>
