<p class="ft2611" style="position:absolute;top:738px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap">(C) All approvals, permits and licenses have been obtained from the concerned </p>
<p class="ft2611" style="position:absolute;top:760px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap">authorities or third parties that should be obtained in connection with the </p>
