<p class="ft2611" style="position:absolute;top:848px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap">(A) There is no dispute, case, investigation, arbitration or other existing or potential </p>
<p class="ft2611" style="position:absolute;top:870px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap">proceeding that would adversely affect the Second Party ’s ability to perform its </p>
<p class="ft2611" style="position:absolute;top:892px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap">obligations under this Contract. </p>
<p class="ft2611" style="position:absolute;top:914px;left:106px;white-space:nowrap"> </p>
<p class="ft2611" style="position:absolute;top:914px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap">(B) There are no court rulings, decisions, or similar orders from any competent </p>
<p class="ft2611" style="position:absolute;top:936px;left:168px;white-space:nowrap">authority against the Second Party that would negatively affect the ability of the </p>
