<p class="ft4112" style="position:absolute;top:488px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap">Without prejudice to any rights or obligations incurred prior to the date of termination </p>
<p class="ft4112" style="position:absolute;top:510px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap">of this Contract, the undertakings and obligations of the Parties stated in the related </p>
<p class="ft4112" style="position:absolute;top:532px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap">Contract clauses, which include but not limited to below items, shall survive after the </p>
<p class="ft4112" style="position:absolute;top:554px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap">expiry or termination of the Contract: </p>
<p class="ft4111" style="position:absolute;top:576px;left:83px;white-space:nowrap"><b> </b></p>
<p class="ft4112" style="position:absolute;top:576px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap">  (A) Clause (24-3) (Confidentiality and Protection of Information). </p>
<p class="ft4111" style="position:absolute;top:598px;left:83px;white-space:nowrap"><b> </b></p>
<p class="ft4112" style="position:absolute;top:598px;left:144px;white-space:nowrap">  (B) Clause (8) (Work Quality Warranty Assurance). </p>
<p class="ft4112" style="position:absolute;top:620px;left:162px;white-space:nowrap">(C) Clause (21) (Intellectual Property rights and protection). </p>
<p class="ft4113" style="position:absolute;top:642px;left:83px;white-space:nowrap"><b>24-14 </b></p>
