<p class="ft4510" style="position:absolute;top:46px;left:293px;white-space:nowrap"><b>General Ts &amp; Cs Contract</b></p>
<p class="ft4510" style="position:absolute;top:46px;left:278px;white-space:nowrap"><b> </b></p>
<p class="ft4511" style="position:absolute;top:115px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap">issued in the future in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia. DACO, its subsidiaries, and the NCA also </p>
<p class="ft4511" style="position:absolute;top:136px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap">have the right to conduct a compliance check to ensure the second party’s compliance with </p>
<p class="ft4511" style="position:absolute;top:158px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap">cybersecurity. </p>
<p class="ft4512" style="position:absolute;top:180px;left:56px;white-space:nowrap"><b> </b></p>
<p class="ft4511" style="position:absolute;top:180px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap">(7) The cybersecurity requirements for contracts and agreements with IT outsourcing. </p>
<p class="ft4512" style="position:absolute;top:202px;left:56px;white-space:nowrap"><b> </b></p>
<p class="ft4512" style="position:absolute;top:202px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap"><b>(D) Architecture Requirements </b></p>
<p class="ft4512" style="position:absolute;top:224px;left:56px;white-space:nowrap"><b> </b></p>
<p class="ft4511" style="position:absolute;top:224px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap">(1) The Solution shall have a privacy module that includes the regulations, standards, and laws </p>
<p class="ft4511" style="position:absolute;top:246px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap">around the platform. </p>
<p class="ft4512" style="position:absolute;top:268px;left:56px;white-space:nowrap"><b> </b></p>
<p class="ft4511" style="position:absolute;top:268px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap">(2) The Solution shall have a Disaster Recovery (DR) dedicated instance. </p>
<p class="ft4512" style="position:absolute;top:290px;left:56px;white-space:nowrap"><b> </b></p>
<p class="ft4511" style="position:absolute;top:290px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap">(3) The Solution shall provide capability for backup configurations. </p>
<p class="ft4512" style="position:absolute;top:312px;left:56px;white-space:nowrap"><b> </b></p>
<p class="ft4511" style="position:absolute;top:312px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap">(4) The Solution shall support high availability. </p>
<p class="ft4512" style="position:absolute;top:334px;left:56px;white-space:nowrap"><b> </b></p>
<p class="ft4511" style="position:absolute;top:334px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap">(5) The Solution shall support whole disk encryption with strong encryption algorithm. </p>
<p class="ft4512" style="position:absolute;top:356px;left:56px;white-space:nowrap"><b> </b></p>
<p class="ft4512" style="position:absolute;top:356px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap"><b>(E)</b> <b>Privacy Requirements</b> </p>
<p class="ft4512" style="position:absolute;top:378px;left:56px;white-space:nowrap"><b> </b></p>
<p class="ft4511" style="position:absolute;top:378px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap">(1)  The  Solution  shall  have  encryption  standard,  algorithm,  and  key  lengths,  for  both </p>
<p class="ft4511" style="position:absolute;top:400px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap">symmetric and asymmetric encryption, compatible with the different components. Refer to </p>
<p class="ft4511" style="position:absolute;top:422px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap">IS-GI-022 Cryptography General Instructions. </p>
<p class="ft4512" style="position:absolute;top:444px;left:56px;white-space:nowrap"><b> </b></p>
<p class="ft4511" style="position:absolute;top:444px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap">(2) The Solution shall support classification with data classification tools if applicable. </p>
<p class="ft4512" style="position:absolute;top:466px;left:56px;white-space:nowrap"><b> </b></p>
<p class="ft4511" style="position:absolute;top:466px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap">(3) The Solution shall support the Access to system to be supported through security channels </p>
<p class="ft4511" style="position:absolute;top:488px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap">only (e.g. HTTPS, SSH etc.). </p>
<p class="ft4512" style="position:absolute;top:528px;left:56px;white-space:nowrap"><b> </b></p>
<p class="ft4512" style="position:absolute;top:528px;left:116px;white-space:nowrap"><b>Reference </b></p>
